		{"id":"feat_study","type":"text","text":"**Roadmap / Study Tab**\n• 6 Units, 24 Lessons + skill/test nodes\n• Node states: locked / active / completed\n• Bouncing active node with START prompt\n• SRS due-review banner at top\n• Node types: lesson | skill | test\n• Skill nodes → practice routes or grammar\n• Test gates between units\n• Redo completed nodes\n• Dialect-aware audio playback","x":160,"y":-780,"width":290,"height":210,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"feat_dict","type":"text","text":"**Dictionary Tab**\n• EN↔VN + ZH↔VN modes\n• 758K EN-VN / 91K ZH-VN entries\n• Hán Việt (Chinese character roots)\n• TTS audio per word\n• Example sentences w/ translation\n• Grammatical explanation\n• 🔴 Long-press icon: Camera OCR\n• 🔴 Long-press icon: Voice search\n• Save words → SRS queue","x":160,"y":-700,"width":290,"height":210,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"feat_library","type":"text","text":"**Library Tab** (Spotify-style filter)\n• Primary type chips: Grammar · Readings · Practice · Vocabulary\n• Sub-tags: A1/A2/B1 · Culture/Food/Travel · Tones/Pronouns/Numbers/Typing · Saved/Custom Decks/Pre-built\n• Sort: Recent / Name / Level\n• View: List / Grid toggle\n• Tap word → dictionary lookup\n• Flashcard decks live here (not standalone route)\n• `dictSavedWords.js` — save/deck management","x":160,"y":-490,"width":290,"height":230,"color":"5"},
