		{"id":"pm_flashcards","type":"text","text":"🃏 **Flashcards / SRS** (in Library tab)\nVocabulary sub-tag in Library\n`/practice/flashcards` → redirects to /practice\nDue items from completed lessons\n`dictSavedWords.js` — custom decks","x":530,"y":-285,"width":290,"height":90,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"pm_teencode","type":"text","text":"💬 **Teen Code** `/practice/teencode`\nVietnamese texting abbreviations\nk=không, dc=được, r=rồi, mk=mình\nCategory drills: basics, pronouns, verbs, internet","x":530,"y":-175,"width":290,"height":90,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"gl_hdr","type":"text","text":"## Lesson Game Loop\n`/lesson/:lessonId`","x":-590,"y":-140,"width":270,"height":60},
		{"id":"gl_exercises","type":"text","text":"**Exercise Types**\n• `mcq` — Multiple choice question\n• `listen_choose` — Audio + pick meaning\n• `reorder` — Drag words into order\n• `diacritics` — Fill in tone marks\n• `dictation` — Hear → type Vietnamese\n• `match_pairs` — Match VN↔EN pairs\n• `speaking_repeat` — Record & compare","x":-600,"y":-60,"width":300,"height":185,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"gl_loop","type":"text","text":"**In-Game Loop**\n1. Load exercises for lesson\n2. Show exercise one by one\n3. Track correct / wrong per Q\n4. Deduct ❤️ on wrong answers\n5. Show streak counter for combos\n6. Give immediate feedback","x":-240,"y":-60,"width":280,"height":180,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"gl_completion","type":"text","text":"**Completion Screen**\n• Final score display\n• Base XP + accuracy bonus\n• Perfect lesson bonus\n• Streak bonus breakdown\n• Vocabulary learned list (VN+EN)\n• Call: `completeNode(nodeId)`","x":-600,"y":155,"width":290,"height":150,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"gl_reward","type":"text","text":"**Rewards Issued**\n• 🪙 Coins added (DongContext)\n• 🔥 Streak maintained\n• nodeSessionCount++ for this node\n• Next roadmap node unlocked after 4 sessions\n• 📚 Words added to SRS queue\n*DongCoin UI + RewardToast removed*","x":-240,"y":155,"width":280,"height":150,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"grammar_list","type":"text","text":"**Grammar List** `/grammar/:level`\n• CEFR levels: A1 → B2\n• VNME's own level scale\n• 13,000+ grammar entries\n• Searchable & filterable","x":90,"y":-60,"width":280,"height":105,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"grammar_detail","type":"text","text":"**Grammar Detail** `/grammar/:level/:index`\n• Rule explanation in EN/ZH\n• Usage formula / sentence pattern\n• Example sentences with TTS audio\n• Tabular comparisons (North/South)\n• Related grammar points","x":90,"y":65,"width":280,"height":115,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"gl_grammar_lesson","type":"text","text":"**Grammar Lesson Node**\n`/grammar-lesson/:nodeId`\n(Triggered from Roadmap skill node)\n• Embeds grammar point directly\n• Awards XP on completion\n• Marks node completed in DongContext","x":90,"y":200,"width":280,"height":100,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"srs_hdr","type":"text","text":"## SRS Review System\n(Spaced Repetition)","x":450,"y":-140,"width":270,"height":60},
		{"id":"srs_engine","type":"text","text":"**SRS Engine** (`srs.js`)\n• Intervals: 1→3→7→14→30 days\n• Cards keyed by item ID in localStorage\n• `addItemsFromLesson(id)` — add on complete\n• `getDueItems()` — fetch what's due today\n• `recordReview(id, correct)` — advance/reset\n• Correct → advance interval\n• Wrong → reset to Day 1","x":440,"y":-60,"width":470,"height":230,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"unit_test","type":"text","text":"**Unit Test Gate** `/test/:nodeId`\n• End-of-unit comprehensive quiz\n• Mix of vocab + grammar exercises\n• Must pass to unlock next unit\n• Failing allows retry\n• Awards bonus XP on pass","x":100,"y":320,"width":280,"height":110,"color":"3"},
